data.description: Great 5 bedroom house in Perris, will be in move in condition. Great family kitchen with walk in pantry breakfast area and center island great for entertaining guest. house has 1 bedroom 1 bathroom downstairs which will be ideal for a family that would be unable to use the stairs. the other 4 bedrooms are all located upstairs. master bedroom has a private bath with oval tub and glass enclosed shower. upstairs also consist of a very comfortable loft home office and game room. Lets not forget the family back yard, great for gatherings and entertainments.
